          <title>First female Kentucky Derby jockey Diane Crump dead at 77</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Pioneering jockey Diane Crump, who broke barriers as the first female rider in the Kentucky Derby in 1970, has died at 77 after a battle with brain cancer.]]></description>
